'''布氏擬龜'''（[[學名|學名]]：''Emys blandingii'' 或 ''Emydoidea blandingii''）<ref name="Rhodin11" /><ref name="Rhodin105-6"/> 是[[澤龜科|澤龜科]]下的一種半水生龜，在[[北美|北美]]的很多地區都是瀕危物種。

== 分類學 ==
在學術期刊上[[擬龜屬|擬龜屬]]被正式作為其所屬。<ref name="Rhodin11" /><ref name="Rhodin138-9"/>

== 生活習性 ==

布氏擬龜主要分佈在[[五大湖|五大湖區]]，并包括更遠的[[內布拉斯加州|內布拉斯加州]]、[[明尼蘇達州|明尼蘇達州]]、<ref name="Minnesota proposed">{{cite web|title=Minnesota State Symbols—Unofficial, Proposed, or Facetious|url=http://www.leg.state.mn.us/leg/unsym.aspx|publisher=Minnesota State Legislature|accessdate=2011-02-25|archive-date=2018-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181224225203/https://www.leg.state.mn.us/leg/unsym|dead-url=no}}</ref> [[紐約|紐約]]、[[新英格蘭|新英格蘭]]和[[新斯科舍省|新斯科舍省]]。<ref>Ernst, C.H., R.W. Barbour, and J.E. Lovich. 1994. Turtles of the United States and Canada. Smithsonian Institution, Washington. p. 242.</ref> 這種龜一般生活在乾淨的淺水濕地中。

== 保護 ==

該物種受到棲息地破壞和[[外來物種|外來物種]]的威脅，<ref name=iucn/> 因而被[[IUCN紅色名錄|IUCN紅色名錄]]<ref name=iucn/> 和[[加拿大|加拿大]]和[[美國|美國]]的一些地區列為瀕危或受威脅物種。<ref name=312iac>{{Cite web|author=Indiana Legislative Services Agency|year=2011|title=312 IAC 9-5-4: Endangered species of reptiles and amphibians|work=Indiana Administrative Code|accessdate=28 Apr 2012|url=http://www.in.gov/legislative/iac/|archive-date=2019-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190809211551/http://www.in.gov/legislative/iac/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>[http://www.michigan.gov/dnr/0,1607,7-153-10370_12145_12201-60647--,00.html Blanding's Turtle] {{Wayback|url=http://www.michigan.gov/dnr/0,1607,7-153-10370_12145_12201-60647--,00.html |date=20171018191348 }}, DNR, Michigan</ref> <ref>[http://www.sararegistry.gc.ca/species/speciesDetails_e.cfm?sid=846 : Blanding's Turtle Great Lakes / St. Lawrence population] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sararegistry.gc.ca/species/speciesDetails_e.cfm?sid=846 |date=20130610232130 }}, Species At Risk Public Registry</ref><ref>[http://www.sararegistry.gc.ca/species/speciesDetails_e.cfm?sid=276 Blanding's Turtle Nova Scotia Population] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sararegistry.gc.ca/species/speciesDetails_e.cfm?sid=276 |date=20130610224620 }}, Species At Risk Public Registry .</ref>

